<subSubSection id="8316FCF6AB57457A4D1CB3787B3EFF1A" pageId="null" pageNumber="192" type="vernacular_names">
<paragraph id="DF25E6F5E93B401411C17E272902B954" pageId="null" pageNumber="192">Halbstrauchiger Ehrenpreis</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
</title>
<subSubSection id="3EBF026FF043C1B0FFA32A25FC433F6B" pageId="null" pageNumber="192" type="description">
<paragraph id="0CB5DB00D7475A3C19AB7CBEAE3C635C" pageId="null" pageNumber="192">
10-25 cm hoch. 
<normalizedToken id="6919740C0B27379991D3BE2126939BA4" originalValue="Blätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="192">Blaetter</normalizedToken>
bis 2,5 cm lang und 0,7 cm breit, die obern 3-8mal so lang wie breit. 
<emphasis id="84A9915235F708B4A485ABF138586769" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="192">
<normalizedToken id="CA794B9CAAB8ED20617B39B5BC30D494" originalValue="Blütenstand" pageId="null" pageNumber="192">Bluetenstand</normalizedToken>
ziemlich dicht
</emphasis>
, 
<emphasis id="9E32A8A0DB12E20DE52DE66A2ABF75E5" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="192">5</emphasis>
- 
<emphasis id="1895EF84D1DC89E91D0754B8639D074F" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="192">20</emphasis>
(
<emphasis id="F7327D948A57E00870084189BE8AB73A" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="192">meist 8</emphasis>
- 
<emphasis id="E777F119416466068C7BEB06DDA88B6E" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="192">13</emphasis>
) 
<emphasis id="70849A748B2A9CEB2AEE7845F8D5A0C9" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="192">
<normalizedToken id="026945D20CE12825CD9DF814838D1506" originalValue="blütig" pageId="null" pageNumber="192">bluetig</normalizedToken>
. Kelch und 
<normalizedToken id="1CC29A2C37CCCCDD62DB1BBC1FE3422D" originalValue="Blütenstiele" pageId="null" pageNumber="192">Bluetenstiele</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="11D07C6547869C53385DE8AFCA689375" originalValue="drüsig" pageId="null" pageNumber="192">druesig</normalizedToken>
behaart. Krone 
<normalizedToken id="A67D1FB8132FFC39DC453A600C23A3BF" originalValue="blaßrosa" pageId="null" pageNumber="192">blassrosa</normalizedToken>
</emphasis>
(selten 
<normalizedToken id="B2FEAEC5F626EC32606713DBC8F585DF" originalValue="weiß" pageId="null" pageNumber="192">weiss</normalizedToken>
), 
<emphasis id="F2E7C2F73254DBF4F32D6EC4F1F80F5F" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="192">
mit dunkleren Adern. Fruchtstiele nur wenig 
<normalizedToken id="66F83208B33CA1BDE8F26BD7FCB7BE7D" originalValue="länger" pageId="null" pageNumber="192">laenger</normalizedToken>
als der Kelch.
</emphasis>
Frucht 5-7 mm lang und 4-5 mm breit. Griffel etwa so lang wie die Frucht. - 
<normalizedToken id="05F213E10648A5001FE6871881645C80" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="192">Bluete</normalizedToken>
: Sommer.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="FD2F4528B2151D911FB7B846CB5ACDAE" pageId="null" pageNumber="192">
<emphasis id="6CE4151ED3AE5BB1758E36417880987A" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="192">Zytologische Angaben. 2n</emphasis>
= 
<emphasis id="5F2D3FB60DFE69B1942CEA797D7F8DC2" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="192">16:</emphasis>
Material aus botanischen 
<normalizedToken id="B45FCF0464DEFC28EF347F9605C6A41B" originalValue="Gärten" pageId="null" pageNumber="192">Gaerten</normalizedToken>
(Simonet 1934b, Beatus 1936, Afanasiyeva und Meshkova 1961).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="E2370162929191D81FE25CE2AFD08898" pageId="null" pageNumber="192">
<emphasis id="AEDCDBF7C398D8C9A0C0CE4297349F84" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="192">Standort.</emphasis>
Subalpin, seltener montan. Kalkreiche 
<normalizedToken id="83E0A3736A16EA4615250EA577682FF6" originalValue="Schüttböden" pageId="null" pageNumber="192">Schuettboeden</normalizedToken>
in sonnigen Lagen. Felsspalten, Schutthalden. 
<emphasis id="909A0F320750B3A52082E94DF3413D43" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="192">Potentillo-Hieracietum</emphasis>
Br.-Bl. 1933.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="B696AD1B5EEEEE1B88C92C53B69721A7" pageId="null" pageNumber="192">
<emphasis id="25FF96EA85065BFBBE7E3543B8A455B3" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="192">
Verbreitung. Mittel- und 
<normalizedToken id="A31D4BB49D1F9E2CEC2D76C25EF1F05B" originalValue="südeuropäische" pageId="null" pageNumber="192">suedeuropaeische</normalizedToken>
Gebirgspflanze:
</emphasis>
Nordspanische Gebirge, 
<normalizedToken id="A9743ADFEDB5D8AC5E64F483A1F453A3" originalValue="Pyrenäen" pageId="null" pageNumber="192">Pyrenaeen</normalizedToken>
, Jura, Alpen, Korsika, Nordapennin, Kroatien, Dalmatien. - Im Gebiet: Alpen, Jura (
<normalizedToken id="04014FDD20E989656C6C59129DB42A55" originalValue="nordwärts" pageId="null" pageNumber="192">nordwaerts</normalizedToken>
bis 
<normalizedToken id="FDAD984F285D68BF094677312A13533D" originalValue="Vallée" pageId="null" pageNumber="192">Vallee</normalizedToken>
de Joux); nicht 
<normalizedToken id="FFF9F07F3F79E7A4CBCFBECD2F8896CD" originalValue="häufig" pageId="null" pageNumber="192">haeufig</normalizedToken>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
